# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your own keys.
# Vite exposes any var prefixed with VITE_ to the browser — so ONLY put client-safe values here.
#
# The model key (Anthropic) is NOT here on purpose: it lives in server/.env and never reaches the
# browser. The client talks to the agent only through the /api proxy. (The old VITE_OPENAI_API_KEY
# was removed in Phase 1 — it used to ship in the bundle, which is exactly the leak the proxy fixes.)
#
# Restrict this Maps key by HTTP referrer + API in the Google Cloud console (see README/SECURITY).
VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=your-google-maps-js-api-key
